# Install
[+]```[/+][-] ```sh[/-]
curl -L -o pop[+] "https://dl.pipecdn.app/v0.2.8/pop"[/+][-] "https://dl.pipecdn.app/v0.2.6/pop"[/-]
```
#
```
chmod +x pop
```
# Make Directory
```
mkdir download_cache
```
# Sign-up With Command
```
./pop --signup-by-referral-route d93ec7a125f095ab
```
# Start The Node
```
sudo ./pop --ram 8 --max-disk 500 --cache-dir /data --pubKey <KEY>[+] --enable-80-443[/+]
```
